title: Liquid Child
text:
Liquid Child were a German dance music production duo, comprising Tobias Menguser and JÃ¼rgen Herbath.  They had chart success in 1999, when they reached #25 in the UK Singles Chart with "Diving Faces". Their next single release was "Return of Atlantis" (1999) which was remixed by Ferry Corsten.
